quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  61,1,"Sabbaha lillahi ma fee assamawatiwama fee al-ardi wahuwa alAAazeezu alhakeem"
  61,2,"Ya ayyuha allatheena amanoolima taqooloona ma la tafAAaloon"
  61,3,"Kabura maqtan AAinda Allahi antaqooloo ma la tafAAaloon"
  61,4,"Inna Allaha yuhibbu allatheenayuqatiloona fee sabeelihi saffan kaannahum bunyanunmarsoos"
  61,5,"Wa-ith qala moosaliqawmihi ya qawmi lima tu/thoonanee waqadtaAAlamoona annee rasoolu Allahi ilaykum falamma zaghooazagha Allahu quloobahum wallahu layahdee alqawma alfasiqeen"